data.description: Beautiful 3-Bedroom Manufactured Home in the Highly-Desirable Farm Community of Wildomar! Open modern-concept layout w/ vaulted ceilings. Spacious living room. Dining area w/ ceiling fan. Kitchen w/ dine-in bar. Master bedroom/bath w/ soaking tub. Large backyard w/ covered patio - perfect for entertaining! Huge driveway w/ extended covered carport & plenty of parking. Laundry room w/ storage. Fully gated lot. Fully paid-off solar system. Community amenities include common areas, citrus groves, amphitheater, 3 swimming pools, 2 spas, catch & release pond, baseball/soccer field, basketball court, tennis court, RV storage areas, hiking trails, &  picnic areas. Low Monthly HOA dues. Needs a little TLC to be the perfect home!
